Simulating the noise and generating data for 12 subjects in a list called subjects


y_count <- nrow(NeuralResponses)
x_count <- ncol(NeuralResponses)

subjects <- list()
for (index in 1:12){
  noise_dist <- matrix(rnorm(x_count*y_count,mean=0,sd=1),y_count,x_count)
  data_with_noise <- noise_dist + NeuralResponses
  subjects[[length(subjects)+1]] <- data_with_noise
}
